    <stitle>5 SPEED AND 6 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON SERIES - REMOVE - SHIFTER HOUSING</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="1">
        <title>SHIFTER HOUSING</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>There are two (2) sizes of bolts. The 1-1/2" bolts are used with the lifting eyes. Note their
                    location.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Shift transmission into neutral position.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the retaining bolts from the shifter housing rim (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302605">Figure 5</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1302605" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1302605" filename="../figg13/G1302605.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 5. Remove Retaining Bolts From Shifter Housing Rim, Break Gasket Seal, and Remove
                    Shifter Housing
                </caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">To break the gasket seal, jar the shifter housing (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302605">Figure 5</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the shifter housing (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302605">Figure 5</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the gasket and clean all mounting surfaces of gasket material.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
